Comment: 0,0:22:46.94,0:24:15.99,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}ED
Comment: 0,0:24:17.95,0:24:21.90,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{\pos(428,163)}Skies of the Rainy Season - Glass Rainbow {tsuyu no sora hari no niji: tsuyu-rainy season; / hari-(Buddhist term) quartz; glass}{http://jisho.org/words?jap=&eng=quartz&dict=edict&romaji=on}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:52.11,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That sound could wake the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.37,0:03:01.28,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Itadakimasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.93,0:03:08.15,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.39,0:03:13.93,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It tastes great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.93,0:03:16.41,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yes, it's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:19.59,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Well, it's not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:21.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:24.34,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}This is a local dish from my village.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:29.17,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Is this thing you call "miso" made the same way as soy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.17,0:03:29.88,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.88,0:03:32.94,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I brought some of the miso my mother made.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:35.49,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}There's a lot more,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.49,0:03:37.59,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}so please eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:44.08,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}To Treize?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:44.79,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:48.39,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}We've finally received notification about our supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:52.79,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Kureha-chan and I will go sign for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:58.14,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}We're running low on ammunition, medicine and various daily supplies, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:04:01.46,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}We can finally relax a little now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.46,0:04:02.95,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Where is Noel going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:04.78,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Carl-san's studio, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:05.27,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.86,0:04:07.31,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:08.28,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:12.62,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}We'll have some intensive trumpet practice this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:15.35,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You really mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.94,0:04:52.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Food's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:54.99,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Geez, how improper...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.99,0:04:58.42,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Your father would cry if he saw that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:02.84,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Like I care.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:14.02,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Have a snack with your tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:18.28,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Fortune cookies, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:21.16,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You still don't like them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.16,0:05:24.51,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The kids at the church weren't responsible, were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:29.56,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The way they demand money for their useless superstitions,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.56,0:05:31.45,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}it's the same as everywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:34.56,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Oh my, that's not true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:36.99,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}At least these are really delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.50,0:05:41.61,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:53.62,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Kana-chan seems like she fits in already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:56.97,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's cute how she always tries so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.97,0:05:58.22,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.22,0:06:01.34,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'll acknowledge her zeal and diligence,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:05.98,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}but it's not that easy to get by with those qualities alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:11.63,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What's with that expression?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.63,0:06:13.32,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's a secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:16.95,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.95,0:06:18.86,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That's so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:30.86,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Well then, off we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:33.61,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'll be back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.61,0:06:34.48,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:36.33,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.97,0:06:40.41,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Don't cause any trouble for Rio-sempai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:43.52,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Commencing departure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:50.35,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Have a good trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:07:00.59,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I don't expect you to get this right away,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:04.56,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}but you basically have to control the sound with only your mouthpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:06.04,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.44,0:07:12.22,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:20.21,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}How is life at base for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:21.85,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:26.60,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Typical of you to be so easygoing about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:28.49,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm a bit envious of your optimism, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:35.90,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Come to think of it, why did you join the army?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:37.89,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:42.92,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Um... I heard that I could learn to play a musical instrument for free...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:49.32,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But, I know that it's important to protect the c-country!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:53.95,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Doesn't bother me, even if it was for money or whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:59.90,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Those with a clear goal in mind will usually last longer than those who don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.32,0:08:03.96,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Um... That's very kind of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:09.23,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Then, why did you join, Rio-sempai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:12.21,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.21,0:08:13.47,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:16.95,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I guess my reason's the opposite of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:20.36,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But that's rare these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:24.95,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Especially for brass instruments, you hardly hear them outside of the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:28.29,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I heard it a long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:32.13,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}A sound similar to yours, Sempai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.13,0:08:32.98,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.98,0:08:37.14,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The sound of the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:46.35,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:47.46,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:48.57,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Hang in there, Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:52.87,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.17,0:09:03.60,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:08.25,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Please... just stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:09.43,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.53,0:09:12.94,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm hot, Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:14.42,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Are you hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.42,0:09:16.99,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I know... It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:18.47,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.05,0:09:26.82,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Mo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.82,0:09:29.64,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:33.08,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What's wrong, Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:36.68,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.37,0:09:41.66,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I want to eat... snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:45.43,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I understand. Just wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.18,0:09:53.07,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:55.47,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Where's the snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.10,0:09:58.63,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Why would we have any here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:02.54,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:04.03,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.56,0:10:06.83,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:17.61,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}No. That should be my last resort!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:25.51,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Medicine, medicine...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.51,0:10:28.85,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Medicine! Medicine...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:31.42,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:35.42,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{\i0}...running low on many things, right?{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:39.36,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Damn those idiots at the supply base!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:44.45,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:45.35,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.23,0:10:49.89,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What should I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:06.93,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.58,0:12:06.28,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Err... What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:10.23,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Don't tell me the children caused trouble again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:13.84,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Please forgive my rudeness towards you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.84,0:12:15.48,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}So, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.43,0:12:18.36,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Please save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.32,0:12:31.80,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Drink this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:34.13,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:45.25,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Her fever is a little high, but this should bring it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.25,0:12:48.25,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Is it some kind of terrible illness?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.25,0:12:51.57,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I think it could be malaria.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.57,0:12:54.29,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Malaria? But that's a kid's illness...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:13:00.22,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Even adults can get it when they're extremely weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.99,0:13:07.80,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Very often, the kids that we take charge of are inflicted with this illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:12.53,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Even those who appear to be fine can be hit by a fever very suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.53,0:13:16.69,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}She must have been fighting it off this whole time; I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:18.03,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Th-Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.03,0:13:20.86,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Will Kanata get better?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:22.05,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}She won't stay like this forever, will she...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:24.82,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I think she'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.77,0:13:30.57,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.03,0:13:36.36,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}T-Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.07,0:13:38.57,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Err...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:42.07,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}My name is Yumina.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:50.06,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}These herbs have to be boiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.06,0:13:53.09,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Give it to her a little later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:14:00.62,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Uh, thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:03.26,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Please, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.26,0:14:09.03,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Caring for the people of this town is our joy and our duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:14.12,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}May you be blessed with good fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:21.14,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}My gratitude for your cooperation!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:14.27,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.09,0:16:20.20,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.52,0:16:25.49,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.03,0:16:28.46,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.36,0:16:39.78,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm just like "omiso".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.78,0:16:41.27,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The stuff we had this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:42.60,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:44.62,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Miso dregs...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.62,0:16:48.03,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}When you make miso soup, you strain the miso...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.03,0:16:50.71,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What remains are the beans and dregs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:54.56,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}An excess baggage, or a burden,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.56,0:16:55.96,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}and so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:59.78,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I've always felt that way, ever since I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.78,0:17:00.46,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.46,0:17:06.25,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I've always wanted to work really hard, so I wouldn't burden anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.95,0:17:08.47,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:15.03,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You are a lot more sensitive than you look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:18.60,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}And also, a selfish, spoiled kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.63,0:17:25.41,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Did... Did I say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.41,0:17:27.51,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Quite a lot... Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:39.41,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That's right, sempai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:41.42,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.42,0:17:43.45,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That song you were just singing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.38,0:17:46.89,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}W-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:48.57,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It goes like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.28,0:18:05.48,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}How astonishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:07.52,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}And she's only heard it once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:09.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}This isn't the first time I've heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:13.22,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I heard it a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:17.02,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I've always wanted to play that song myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:20.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.97,0:18:25.47,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The song that seems to resound from the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.74,0:18:32.79,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But I guess being an omiso, I'll just remain an omiso no matter where I go, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.24,0:18:34.54,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:39.79,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}We can't rely on the church for everything, right
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.41,0:18:43.94,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The Takemikazuchi is a relic from a previous era,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.94,0:18:48.03,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}and inside it sleep many different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.03,0:18:49.31,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Different things?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:53.04,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yeah. You can ask Noel about the details later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.90,0:19:08.52,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}All right, this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:10.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Here it goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.29,0:19:22.94,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.94,0:19:24.32,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}This song!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:06.17,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}This is probably the complete version of the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.17,0:20:12.35,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Many instruments, all coming together in harmony, becoming a single piece of music.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:15.54,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's the same with a tank crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.54,0:20:21.23,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Commander, gunner, driver and communications...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.23,0:20:25.11,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Everyone's efforts come together to mobilize one tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:28.23,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}No one is useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.23,0:20:31.36,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}And every sound is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.99,0:20:39.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Don't look at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:40.37,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I was just repeating...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.37,0:20:45.36,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}...the words of the person I admire and respect the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:49.89,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}To borrow her words... Kanata,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.89,0:20:53.55,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}why do you think sempai or superior officers exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.89,0:20:57.34,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}So that their juniors are able to bother them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.79,0:21:01.59,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It doesn't matter if you can't do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:05.08,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Just remember the frustration and helplessness you felt,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.08,0:21:08.12,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}and how happy you were to be protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.12,0:21:12.60,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}And someday, when you're in a position to protect someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.60,0:21:15.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}this will help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.74,0:21:19.75,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}So, just cause as much trouble as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:21.38,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I did the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.29,0:21:26.50,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Naturally, if you blunder, you'll be scolded and even punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.50,0:21:27.11,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.11,0:21:29.59,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}When it gets too frustrating, say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.59,0:21:30.39,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Even when you're suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.05,0:21:33.63,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.58,0:21:40.63,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.63,0:21:44.48,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}From now on, I'll be sure to cause you lots and {\i1}lots{\i0} of trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:46.49,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:54.62,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Then, just go easy on me, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.13,0:22:01.10,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Aw, jeez... I should've just stayed behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.10,0:22:05.86,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Kanata actually had Rio-sempai nurse her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.86,0:22:09.38,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What? It wasn't that big of a deal,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.38,0:22:11.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}and it was merely due to fatigue.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.01,0:22:12.89,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}She'll be fine if she sleeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.21,0:22:21.54,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Takemikazuchi's lights were on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.54,0:22:23.09,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Ah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.09,0:22:25.30,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I used it for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.30,0:22:27.29,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Was there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.16,0:22:31.14,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You listened to that song, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.98,0:22:32.78,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.77,0:22:36.73,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Didn't you say you never wanted to hear it again though?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.73,0:22:38.29,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I just had a change of heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.81,0:22:43.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}And?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.59,0:22:46.94,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.95,0:24:19.03,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.03,0:24:21.90,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Rainy Season Sky, Quartz Rainbow.
